1. Volim da igram uz *ritam* muzike. (I love to dance to the rhythm of music.)
2. *Ritam* srca se ubrzao kada sam je video. (The rhythm of my heart accelerated when I saw her.)
3. Ovaj *ritam* je veoma spor. (This rhythm is very slow.)
4. Ona je vrlo talentovana za plesni *ritam*. (She is very talented for dance rhythm.)
5. *Ritam* života u ovom gradu je veoma brz. (The rhythm of life in this city is very fast.)
6. Muzički *ritam* je uticao na njen način govora. (The musical rhythm influenced her way of speaking.)
7. *Ritam* ovog benda je veoma zarazan. (The rhythm of this band is very catchy.)
8. Treba da se prilagodimo *ritmu* ovog projekta. (We need to adapt to the rhythm of this project.)
9. Trkački *ritam* je bio veoma zahtevan za ovog sportistu. (The racing rhythm was very demanding for this athlete.)
10. *Ritam* melodije je uvek bio važan u narodnoj muzici. (The rhythm of melody has always been important in folk music.)